definitions.definition: An English surname originating as a patronymic .

subdefinitions.definition: A suburb of Canberra , Australian Capital Territory , Australia .

A place in the United States : An unincorporated community in Lawrence County , Kentucky . A township in Morrison County , Minnesota . A township in Butler County , Nebraska . A city in Dallas County and Collin County , Texas ; an affluent inner suburb of Dallas . An unincorporated community in Calhoun County , West Virginia . An unincorporated community in the town of Clayton , Polk County , Wisconsin .
